            release: { tr: "Push için iki seçenek: <strong>Expo Push API</strong> (en kolay; FCM/APNs konfigürasyonu olmadan kendi backend'inden Expo'ya gönderirsin; token <code>expo-notifications</code>'ın <code>getExpoPushTokenAsync</code>'i ile alınıyor) VEYA <strong>FCM</strong> doğrudan (development build + <code>@react-native-firebase/messaging</code> ya da <code>expo-notifications</code>'ın <code>getDevicePushTokenAsync</code>'i ile native FCM/APNs token). Token backend'e kaydediliyor; test bildirimi geliyor. iOS için <strong>APNs key</strong> Expo Dashboard'da veya Firebase Console'da yüklü; Android 13+ için <code>POST_NOTIFICATIONS</code> izni <code>expo-notifications</code> ile alınıyor.", en: "Two push options: the <strong>Expo Push API</strong> (the easiest; send from your backend to Expo with no FCM/APNs config; token retrieved via <code>expo-notifications</code>' <code>getExpoPushTokenAsync</code>) OR <strong>FCM</strong> directly (development build + <code>@react-native-firebase/messaging</code>, or a native FCM/APNs token via <code>expo-notifications</code>' <code>getDevicePushTokenAsync</code>). Tokens are saved to the backend; test notifications arrive. The <strong>APNs key</strong> is uploaded in the Expo Dashboard or Firebase Console for iOS; on Android 13+, the <code>POST_NOTIFICATIONS</code> permission is requested via <code>expo-notifications</code>." }
